{
  "stem": "717.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "In fact, there were rumors already that some people came back and they saw the elderly people are being taking care of beautifully-- beautiful food, they don't even need to work, and the children are being taken care.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "People said.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You never saw who saw it, but you heard, somebody heard from somebody that saw it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they took us to the jail, which was right around the corner from where we lived, [INAUDIBLE] Jail.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I think we stayed there overnight, and then they marched us to the train station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't even remember whether that was-- it was in Magazyn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was somewhere near the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they put us in the box cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of people was packed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There was hardly room to sit down or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And they put a huge can in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "This was supposed to the toilet, men and women together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they closed the-- the box cars, and we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I was with my mother then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And just to show how nice the Germans are, everybody go they can of conserved pork with all the fat in it, as you going away present.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Nobody thought about-- I mean, at that time, we didn't worry about cholesterol.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So of course we ate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when you eat this kind of fat-- it was just fat-- this-- I don't whether everybody-- in our wagon I know we got that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Everybody got diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you had that can, somewhere on the corner, or on the middle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how long it took us to go to Birkenau, but we arrived there at dawn, because I remember it was still dark.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
